<p data-start="1060" data-end="1254">Töltsd fel a ZIP‑et egy olyan tárhelyre, ami nem blokkolja az iframe / JavaScript‑et — például GitHub Pages. Ez ingyenes és egyszerű statikus weboldalakhoz. <span class="" data-state="closed"><span class="ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]" data-testid="webpage-citation-pill"><a href="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/git/using-github-to-host-a-free-static-website/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" alt="https://www.geeksforgeeks.org/git/using-github-to-host-a-free-static-website/?utm_source=chatgpt.com" class="flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]!"><span class="relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center"><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between" style="opacity: 1; transform: none;"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">GeeksforGeeks</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+2</span></span><span class="flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute" style="opacity: 0; transform: translateX(10%);"><span class="max-w-[15ch] grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center">MDN Web Docs</span><span class="-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]">+2</span></span></span></a></span></span></p>
